title: What is your favorite punch line from K-pop rappers? - Quora

response.answer_text: These aren't exactly going to be catchphrases that are used often. Some of them were just used in perhaps one song, but I always tend to remember it.  ATEEZ's Mingi’s ‘Fix On’ before most of his rap verses. In their song, ‘Wonderland’, you can hear it after the first chorus, at the start of the second verse.  I.M’s ‘I.M what I am’ before his verse in ‘Shootout’. Also Joohoney’s ‘Joohunnit One Hunnit’.  Joohoney’s ‘Baby, Who the X? I'm a X’ in ‘Jealousy’.  NCT 127’s Mark’s ‘Long ass ride’. He's used it a few times, but I've only heard it in Whiplash. (I haven't heard that many of their songs).  JBJ95’s Sanggyun’s ‘Swerve, baby’ before majority of his rap verses. He used it a lot in his JBJ days and continues to use it now in JBJ95. (Descriptions are under videos.)
